data.description: Great 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home in the community of ''West Gate'' with a large, fenced back yard and 2 car garage. Main level complete with living room open to the eat in area and kitchen plus dining room.The second level offers 3 bedrooms with laundry room and two full baths. Amenities include a clubhouse, pool complex with splash pad, gym, playground, soccer field and volleyball courts ... all for $33.00 a month.Great neighborhood for walkng or biking.
